# Project Overview and Navigation

- Linkp is a link-in-bio platform for Indian content creators, with a brand-creator promotional marketplace, deep analytics, and a code-first template system.
- The project is a monorepo with a Next.js frontend (`apps/linkp-website`) and a Cloudflare Worker backend API (`apps/linkp-worker`).
- For roadmap, features, and priorities, see [project-progress.md](mdc:project-progress.md).
